        "subject": "LU-3557 mdt: fix open existing file with O_CREAT for ro mount",
        "message": "LU-3557 mdt: fix open existing file with O_CREAT for ro mount\n\nWe should only return -EROFS for read only mount if we really\nneed to create the file in question.\n\nDefer the check to mdt_reint_open() instead of mdt_intent_opc().\n\nBackported from 9a2bdd6ca1e441e3b019725c30dc460be0853216\n\nSigned-off-by: Shuichi Ihara <sihara@ddn.com>\nSigned-off-by: Li Dongyang <dongyang.li@anu.edu.au>\nChange-Id: I9eaed3954f04246c3f821ff39f2ded6deaedf68d\n"
